Astro

from BUSINESS TIMES, The New Straits Times Press (Malaysia) Berhad,
     30 Sep 1996, page 6

A COOL RM1 billion would have been invested to bring Malaysians the
region's first direct-to-user satellite broadcast services called Astro,
or All Asia Television and Radio Company.
  Half of the amount has already been spent to set up the ALL Asia
Broadcast Centre at Bukit Jalil, Kuala Lumpur. The other half a billion
ringgit would be spent in the next few years.
                               

