Urging the Americans to ... 

from BUSINESS TIMES, The New Straits Times Press (Malaysia) Berhad,
     30 Sep 1996, page 6

URGING the Americans to "give us a break," Prime Minister Datuk Seri Dr
Mahathir Mohamad invited them to "go west ... or what you call the East"
and be "our partner in the development and dynamism and help in the making
of a prosperous Asia".
  SHARP fall on September 26 in the prices of second board counters caught
many players by surprise, although there have been calls for caution by
some market observers.
  The second board index tumbled 24.86 points of 3.98 per cent to end the
day at 605.55 even though the Kuala Lumpur Stock Exchange Composite Index
ease a mere 0.5 points to 1,128.81.
                               

