Meeting on motorsport row

from BUSINESS TIMES, The New Straits Times Press (Malaysia) Berhad,
     30 Sep 1996, page 2

YOUTH and Sports Minister Tan Sri Muhyiddin Mohd Yassin says Automobile
Association of Malaysia (AAM) chairman Tunku Mudzaffar Tunku Mustapha has
written to him requesting that they meet with local motorsport officials
over alleged infighting and disputes within the affiliates. Speaking in
Subang yesterday after opening the national level "Jati Diri Budaya Belia"
