JANUARY 1996

ISRAEL
BASIC DATA

Head of State. . . . . . . . . . .President Ezer Weizman (since 1993)

Head of Government . . . . . Prime Minister Shimon Peres (since 1992)

Area . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .20,700 sq. km

