<UL>
<A HREF = "#20"><LI>MAD COW DISEASE: MIXED SIGNALS FROM COMMISSION ON "PROVEN" BSE/CJD LINK</A>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp<NOBR>(823 words)</NOBR></LI>
</UL>
